rst cases in [[Udmurtia]] (2 cases), [[Bryansk Oblast]], and [[Novgorod Oblast]] (1 case each).<ref name=\"rusmar22\" />\n\nOn 23 March, 71 new cases were confirmed, all of them in Moscow.<ref name=\"rusmar23\"/>\n\nOn 24 March, 57 new cases were confirmed, including first cases in [[Primorsky Krai]], [[Oryol Oblast]], the [[Chechen Republic]], [[Volgograd Oblast]] and [[Bashkortostan]].<ref name=\"rusmar24\"/>\n\nOn 25 March, 163 new cases were confirmed, 120 of them in Moscow, with first cases in [[Pskov Oblast]] and [[Rostov Oblast]].<ref name=\"rusmar25\"/> 2 deaths were also later reported and confirmed in Moscow. The patients were 73 and 88 years old and had been tested positive for the coronavirus.<ref name=\"tass-deaths-mar25\">{{cite news|url=https://tass.ru/obschestvo/8077753|title=\u0412 \u041c\u043e\u0441\u043a\u0432\u0435 \u0443\u043c\u0435\u0440\u043b\u0438 \u0434\u0432\u0430 \u043f\u043e\u0436\u0438\u043b\u044b\u0445 \u043f\u0430\u0446\u0438\u0435\u043d\u0442\u0430 \u0441 \u043a\u043e\u0440\u043e\u043d\u0430\u0432\u0438\u0440\u0443\u0441\u043e\u043c|agency=[[TASS]]|date=25 March 2020|access-date=25 March 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200325231108/https://tass.ru/obschestvo/8077753|archive-date=25 March 2020|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\nOn 26 March, 182 new cases were confirmed, 136 of them in Moscow, with first cases in [[Buryatia]].<ref name=\"rusmar26\"/> According to a source in the hospital and an official report to the prosecutor office, an 83-year-old woman (a patient of a surgeon who got sick earlier, see 31 March) died in [[Syktyvkar]] of COVID-19, the death was covered up by the local authorities and not included in the official count.<ref>{{cite web |url=https://novayagazeta.ru/news/2020/03/26/160141-istochnik-v-syktyvkare-umerla-pozhilaya-patsientka-s-podtverzhdennym-koronavirusom |title=\u0418\u0441\u0442\u043e\u0447\u043d\u0438\u043a: \u0432 \u0421\u044b\u043a\u0442\u044b\u0432\u043a\u0430\u0440\u0435 \u0443\u043c\u0435\u0440\u043b\u0430 \u043f\u043e\u0436\u0438\u043b\u0430\u044f \u043f\u0430\u0446\u0438\u0435\u043d\u0442\u043a\u0430 \u0441 \u043f\u043e\u0434\u0442\u0432\u0435\u0440\u0436\u0434\u0435\u043d\u043d\u044b\u043c \u043a\u043e\u0440\u043e\u043d\u0430\u0432\u0438\u0440\u0443\u0441\u043e\u043c |publisher=Novayagazeta.ru |date= |accessdate=2020-04-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200327142621/https://novayagazeta.ru/news/2020/03/26/160141-istochnik-v-syktyvkare-umerla-pozhilaya-patsientka-s-podtverzhdennym-koronavirusom |archive-date=27 March 2020 |url-status=live }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.severreal.org/a/30511036.html | title=\u041a\u043e\u043c\u0438: \u043e\u0442 \u043f\u043d\u0435\u0432\u043c\u043e\u043d\u0438\u0438 \u0441\u043a\u043e\u043d\u0447\u0430\u043b\u0430\u0441\u044c \u043f\u0430\u0446\u0438\u0435\u043d\u0442\u043a\u0430, \u0443 \u043a\u043e\u0442\u043e\u0440\u043e\u0439 \u0431\u044b\u043b \u043a\u043e\u0440\u043e\u043d\u0430\u0432\u0438\u0440\u0443\u0441 | access-date=28 March 2020 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200326170550/https://www.severreal.org/a/30511036.html | archive-date=26 March 2020 | url-status=live }}</ref> An official working under the chief of staff of the prime minister also tested positive for the coronavirus that day.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://meduza.io/news/2020/03/26/u-odnogo-iz-sotrudnikov-apparata-pravitelstva-rf-obnaruzhili-koronavirus|title=\u0423 \u0441\u043e\u0442\u0440\u0443\u0434\u043d\u0438\u043a\u0430 \u0430\u043f\u043f\u0430\u0440\u0430\u0442\u0430 \u043f\u0440\u0430\u0432\u0438\u0442\u0435\u043b\u044c\u0441\u0442\u0432\u0430 \u0420\u0424 \u043d\u0430\u0448\u043b\u0438 \u043a\u043e\u0440\u043e\u043d\u0430\u0432\u0438\u0440\u0443\u0441. \"\u0420\u0443\u0441\u0441\u043a\u0430\u044f \u0441\u043b\u0443\u0436\u0431\u0430 \u0411\u0438-\u0431\u0438-\u0441\u0438\" \u0441\u043e\u043e\u0431\u0449\u0438\u043b\u0430 \u043e \u043f\u0440\u0438\u0437\u043d\u0430\u043a\u0430\u0445 \u0438\u043d\u0444\u0435\u