le]] (French, 1821-1859) \n* [[Joseph Austin Benwell]] (British, 1816\u20131886)\n* Narcisse Berch\u00e8re (1819-1891) [[:fr:Narcisse Berch\u00e8re]]<ref>Thornton, L., ''The Orientalists: Painter Travellers,'' [Edition en langue anglaise], Paris, ACR, 1994, pp 29-30</ref>\n* Francisco Lameyer Berenguer (1825-1877)\n* [[\u00c9mile Bernard]] (French, 1868-1941)\n* Mariano Bertuchi y Nieto (Spanish, 1842-1955) <ref>Angl\u00e9s, E.A., \"La Visi\u00f3n de Marruecos a Trav\u00e9s de la Pintura Orientalista Espa\u00f1ola, in: ''Im\u00e1genes Coloniales de Marruecos en Espa\u00f1a,'' 2007, pp 37-41 [https://journals.openedition.org/mcv/2821 Online:] (translated from Spanish)</ref>[[:es:Mariano Bertuchi]]\n* Hippolyte Berteaux (French, 1843-1928)\n* [[Antonio Berti (painter)]] (Italian, 1830-1912)\n* Pierre Marie Beyle (French, 1838-1902)\n* Roger Bezombes (French, 1913-1994) painter, engraver and lithographer [[:fr:Roger Bezombes]]\n* [[Alexandre Bida]] (French, 1813-1895)  \n* Anton 'Tony' Binder (Austrian, 1868-1944) painter and photographer <ref>''Orientalists: postcards of the Holy Land, 1800-1935: from the collection of Yoel Amer,'' 2008, p. 110</ref>\n* [[Gonzalo Bilbao]] (Spanish, 1860-1938)<ref>Angl\u00e9s, E.A., \"La Visi\u00f3n de Marruecos a Trav\u00e9s de la Pintura Orientalista Espa\u00f1ola, in: ''Im\u00e1genes Coloniales de Marruecos en Espa\u00f1a,'' 2007, pp 37-41 [https://journals.openedition.org/mcv/2821 Online:] (translated from Spanish)</ref>\n* [[Cesare Biseo]] (1843-1909)\n* Maurice Bismouth (1891-1965) [[:fr:Maurice Bismouth]]\n* Norbert Bitner (Austrian, 1786-1845)\n* Aurelio Blasco Maicas (Spanish, 1838-1891)<ref>Caso, E.D., ''Les Orientalistes de l'\u00e9cole Espagnole,'' ACR edition, 1997, p. 24</ref>\n* [[Edwin Howland Blashfield]] (American, 1848-1936)<ref>Ackerman, G.M., ''American Orientalists,'' ACR, 1994. pp 16-19</ref>\n* Alexandre Bloch (1857-1919) [[:fr:Alexandre Bloch]]\n* [[Ludwig Blum]] (Israeli, 1891-1975)\n* [[Viktor Bobrov (painter