iss-Hertzig (1895-1968)\n* [[Elena Nikandrovna Klokacheva]] (Russian, 1871-c.1943)\n* Ernst Karl Eugen Koerner (German, 1846-1927) \n* [[Oskar Kokoschka]] (Austrian, 1886-1980)\n* [[Konstantin Korovin]] (Russian, 1861-1939)\n* Franz Xaver Kosler (Austrian, 1864-1905)<ref>Thornton, L., ''The Orientalists: Painter-travellers, 1828-1908,'' Volume 1, ACR \u00c9dition, 1983, p. 242</ref>\n* [[Setsuzo Kotsuji]] (Japanese, 1899-1973) \n* [[Johann Victor Kr\u00e4mer]] (Austrian, 1861-1949) Orientalist photographer and painter\n* [[Ivan Kramskoi]] (Russian, 1837-1887) \n* [[Christian Krohg]] (Norwegian, 1852-1925) \n* [[Pavel Kuznetsov]] (Russian, 1878-1968)\n* [[G\u00fcls\u00fcn  Karamustafa]] (Turkish, b, 1946)\n\n==L==\n* Jos\u00e9 Laguna Perez (Spanish, ?-?)\n* [[Francisco Lameyer|Francisco Lameyer Berenguer]] (Spanish, 1825-1877)<ref>Angl\u00e9s, E.A., \"La Visi\u00f3n de Marruecos a Trav\u00e9s de la Pintura Orientalista Espa\u00f1ola, in: ''Im\u00e1genes Coloniales de Marruecos en Espa\u00f1a,'' 2007, pp 37-41 [https://journals.openedition.org/mcv/2821 Online:] (translated from Spanish)</ref>\n* Evgeny Lanseray (Russian, 1875-1946)<ref>Atroschenko, O., Bulatov, V., Kouteinikova, I., Solovyeva, K. and Schimmelpenninck van der Oye, D., ''Russia's Unknown Orient: Orientalist Painting 1850-1920,'' Nai010 Publishers, 2010</ref>\n* Augustus Osborne Lamplough (British, 1877-1930)<ref>Thornton, L., ''The Orientalists: Painter Travellers,'' [Edition en langue anglaise], Paris, ACR, 1994, p. 118</ref>\n* [[Charles Landelle]] (French, 1821-1908)<ref> Benjamin, R., ''Orientalist Aesthetics: Art, Colonialism, and French North Africa: 1880-1930,'' University of California Press, 2003, p. 60</ref> \n* Georges H. Landelle (French, 1860-1898) \n* [[Jean-Charles Langlois]] (French, 1789-1870) \n* [[Joseph de La N\u00e9zi\u00e8re]] (French, 1873\u20131944) \n* William Laparra (French, 1873-1920) [[:fr:William Laparra]] \n* Jos\u00e9 de la Larrocha Gonz\u00e1lez (Spanish, 1850-1933) \n* 