 delivery possible 24/7.}}\n| Government Resolution No. 211/2020 Coll.<ref name=\"all services banned 14 March\"/>\n\nMinistry of Health Protection Measure No. MZDR 12746/2020-1/MIN/KAN<ref name=\"shops 1 April\">{{cite web|url=https://www.mzcr.cz/Soubor.ashx?souborID=40685&typ=application/pdf&nazev=Mimo%C5%99%C3%A1dn%C3%A9%20opat%C5%99en%C3%AD%20-%20omezen%C3%AD%20maloobchodn%C3%ADho%20prodeje.pdf |title=Info |publisher=mzcr.cz |date= |accessdate=6 April 2020}}</ref>\n\nMinistry of Health Protection Measure No. MZDR 13361/2020-2/MIN/KAN<ref name=\"shops 11 April\"/>\n\nMinistry of Health Protection Measure No. MZDR 15190/2020-3/MIN/KAN<ref name=\"auto\">{{cite web|url=https://www.mzcr.cz/Soubor.ashx?souborID=40881&typ=application/pdf&nazev=Mimo%C5%99%C3%A1dn%C3%A9%20opat%C5%99en%C3%AD%20-%20maloobchodn%C3%AD%20prodej%20a%20prodej%20slu%C5%BEeb%20v%20provozovn%C3%A1ch.pdf |title=Info |publisher=mzcr.cz |date= |accessdate=8 April 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| Public banned from entering premises of selected services.\n\nClosure of all fitness centers, baths, tanning salons, saunas, wellness providers, dance and social clubs, entertainment providers, public libraries, galleries.\n| 12 March 2020\n| From 13 March 6&nbsp;am onwards (indefinitely).\n|\n| Government Resolution No. 199/2020 Coll.<ref name=\"30 people ban\"/>\n|-\n| Tourist information centers closed.\n\nPublic banned from entering tourist information centres and swimming pools.\n| 13 March 2020\n| From 14 March 6&nbsp;am onwards (indefinitely).\n|\n| Government Resolution No. 208/2020 Coll.<ref name=\"info center ban\">{{cite web|url=https://www.vlada.cz/assets/media-centrum/aktualne/DOC130320-130320_208.pdf |title=Info |publisher=vlada.cz |date= |accessdate=6 April 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| Marketplaces closed\n\nBan on retail trade at marketplaces.\n| 13 March 2020\n| From 14 March 6&nbsp;am onwards (indefinitely).\n\n'''Partially revoked on 20 April 2020''' (only outdoors marketplaces)\n| While having a general effect,